  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Experienced full stack web developer, designer, and college professor with expertise in Python, TypeScript, 
    C++, and Kotlin. Skilled in designing and developing responsive web applications 
    using React, Next.js, and Astro. Proficient in cloud technologies such as AWS, Firebase, Google Cloud and
    developing mobile applications on the Android platform.
    With over 20 years of experience working collaboratively with cross-functional teams and providing technical 
    leadership in fast-paced environments. Passionate about exploring emerging technologies 
    and contributing to open-source projects, with experience teaching and mentoring junior 
    developers, designers, and students.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

